data.description: Welcome to this cute 3 bed 2 bath home with tile stretched throughout the house. This home offers a large backyard backed to a wash for enjoyment and a beautiful front lake view. This property boost an abundant amount of parking space on both sides of the home. Whether you have multiple vehicles or frequently host guest, you'll never have to worry about parking availability.
